</style><p>此次hololive SUPER EXPO 2024，女性粉丝和外国粉丝（俗称海外Niki）数量较去年有明显增长。据参观该会场的管理人员透露，他们经常看到“Mikomet（佐仓巫子和星町水星）”的粉丝。</p><p> HoloRêve 的推出可以被视为 Hololive 开发新商品的挑战之一，Hololive 的观众和粉丝数量持续增加，无论性别或国籍如何。</p><p>此外，闭幕式上还公布了新项目“hololive City 24”以及hololive SUPER EXPO 2024快闪店。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="v800Rjgucf"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/hololive-production-hololive-city-24-starts-in-summer-2024-to-be-held-in-6-cities-in-japan/">Hololive Production“Hololive City 24”将于2024年夏季开始，将在日本6个城市举办</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Hololive Production《Hololive City 24》将于 2024 年夏季开始，在日本 6 个城市举办” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/hololive-production-hololive-city-24-starts-in-summer-2024-to-be-held-in-6-cities-in-japan/embed/#?secret=CY5PIJad0p#?secret=v800Rjgucf" data-secret="v800Rjgucf" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="DZlq2kjUDQ"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/hololive-super-expo-2024-pop-up-store-to-be-held-in-6-cities-in-japan/">Hololive SUPER EXPO 2024快闪店将在全国6个城市举办</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“hololive SUPER EXPO 2024快闪店将在全国6个城市举办” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/hololive-super-expo-2024-pop-up-store-to-be-held-in-6-cities-in-japan/embed/#?secret=gjKHT9JaXJ#?secret=DZlq2kjUDQ" data-secret="DZlq2kjUDQ" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p> <a href="https://hololivesuperexpo2024.hololivepro.com/" target="_blank" rel="noref